Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96409,99120}– Good morning, Meimi.\N– Good morning, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:43.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99746,103166}– Another lovely day, isn't it?\N– It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108171,110798}Seira, what's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:55.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111007,115803}Maybe Asuka Jr.'s solved a case\Nand they want his autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116012,118097}That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:05.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122060,125480}Yutaka, please!\NGet your father to sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:09.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125855,129484}But my father's not even an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130318,132779}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:18.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132987,138868}Didn't you know?\NYutaka's father wrote a bestseller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:22.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139118,142580}Oh, really? Seira, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:26.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142789,146793}I bought one. It's titled\NExpedition Journal of Jurassic Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:32.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147418,152006}His father discovered an egg\Nof the legendary bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153091,154759}A legendary bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:40.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155510,160765}GET BACK THE PHANTOM BIRD EGG!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:49.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164352,169691}– Seira, have you read it?\N– Yes, would you like to read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:55.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170733,175780}It looks so hard.\NMaybe I'll just go get his autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:03:02.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176406,182161}Professor Mochizuki, Yutaka's father,\Nis a well-known explorer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182495,185873}He was investigating\Nthe existence of the bird…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186082,189127}…in a jungle\Nin the southern hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189752,192130}And he discovered the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:17.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192755,197802}Yes. A fiery red Apua bird said\Nto have lived on the island ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198010,201055}Then he compiled his report\Ninto a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:27.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201389,207520}Exploring a jungle,\Na fiery red bird. How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214318,216654}A lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:43.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218197,223369}You'll never go exploring the jungle\Nif this little thing scares you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:58.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234338,238134}Mr. Asuka, pets are not allowed\Nin the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:02.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238342,242764}As punishment, you will clean\Nthe birdcage after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245183,246350}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257862,260323}Your father's precious egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:24.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260656,264869}Yes, a Professor Hyuga from\Nthe Scientific Research lnstitute…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:28.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265119,268623}…came by, claiming\Nto be my father's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271834,275797}I'd appreciate you letting me\Nborrow your father's egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:40.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276130,280593}My father's not in tonight.\NCan you wait until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281177,283638}I have his permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283846,286474}I'd like to study the egg…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:50.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286682,290353}…as part of my research\Nof the Apua bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:54.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290603,294023}Why, I promise to return it\Nin two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:59.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294232,299028}He said he'd return it and I let him\Ntake it without thinking it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299612,302990}What? Hyuga took the egg last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303574,306327}Oh, God, I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306536,309288}Dad, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:14.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310206,314585}Yutaka, I made the egg. It's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314794,317922}I painted an ostrich egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318548,322385}Then you lied\Nabout discovering the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:25.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322593,325638}You wrote that book\Nbased on pure fiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325930,329183}No, I'm certain\NI really did find the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329392,332478}Animals are very delicate creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333020,336816}Being tossed around on\Na long ocean voyage to Japan…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337024,338818}…would kill any animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:42.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339026,342822}That egg is priceless,\Nso I didn't bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343030,346993}– I wanted the bird to be raised there.\N– I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347368,352665}But I had to let the world\Nknow of my discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:57.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352874,357837}I needed proof\Nto convince my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:03.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358713,363092}So you made the fake to use as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:08.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363301,368264}But I never imagined my book\Nwould cause such a sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:13.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368514,373936}A man in my position should never have\Nused a fake to prove his discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374145,377315}Then why don't you explain it\Nto everyone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377940,380735}You're right.\NBut of all the bad luck…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380943,384655}…it will be Hyuga\Nwho breaks the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387116,388701}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:34.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389493,394040}Professor Hyuga has always\Ncriticized my father's research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:38.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394248,398961}If he analyzes the egg,\Nhe's sure to realize it's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399170,401589}I need the egg back before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401797,404550}And where is the egg now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404759,407345}Hyuga's Scientific Research lnstitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410181,411891}A fake egg, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412683,417396}Using a fake to prove one's theory\Nis certainly unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:01.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417605,421984}But Professor Mochizuki\Ndeeply regrets it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:06.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422568,426989}And it's too bad Professor Hyuga\Nwill reveal the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:10.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427198,430826}I did some checking and learned\Nthat Professor Hyuga…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431035,434997}…is scheduled to go on TV\Ntomorrow to discuss the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435456,436832}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:21.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437041,441003}You want me to get the egg\Nbefore he analyzes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441253,444382}Brilliant deduction.\NI knew I could count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:33.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448594,453975}Why did she have to stick me\Nwith this dirty job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:40.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456435,460189}I need to clean this place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462149,464443}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:50.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466278,470282}What? "Tonight at 8:00, I am going\Nto Professor Hyuga's lab…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:56.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470491,476539}…to steal the legendary egg.\N– St. Tail." St. Tail's note!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481085,484588}– I'm home!\N– Welcome home, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484797,487383}What's with Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492722,495057}Hi, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495599,497476}Oh, Meimi, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:23.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498102,503357}What's the matter? You promised\Nto show me your trick when I got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503566,506777}I'm sorry. I got so involved\Nwith the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506944,508320}What program?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508487,510740}UNCOVER PARANORMAL PHENOMENA\NWlTH DR. HYUGA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510948,513784}– You know him?\N– Yeah, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:39.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513993,519498}You were saying there is nothing\Nthat is scientifically unexplainable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519707,521333}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:47.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521542,527548}Supernatural phenomena and legendary\Ncreatures do not exist in our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:51.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527757,531469}For example, mirages\Nand a dead person's spirit…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531677,537433}…which so many romanticize about,\Nhave been scientifically explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:01.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538434,541062}This is a mirage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:06.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541270,546275}Isn't it incredible? Even a machine\Nis capable of creating one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546525,548277}And now, to continue…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548486,550946}A dead person's spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:17.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552031,557787}Lately, I've been hearing of fools\Ncausing a sensation by ranting…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:22.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557995,562124}…of miracles and legends,\Nbut I will expose them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562333,565294}This journal is a bestseller, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:30.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565503,570466}Yes. In my professional opinion,\Nthe legendary Apua bird…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:34.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570633,574970}…does not exist anywhere.\NThis book is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:40.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575179,580726}And tomorrow on this program,\Nwe will reveal the infamous egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582019,585689}The egg Professor Mochizuki found\Ncannot be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585898,588359}And I will expose—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588692,589777}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589985,592446}Why'd you turn it off?\NIt was interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:56.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592988,596450}Because I don't like that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596659,599870}The other day at a magic show,\Nthat awful man…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:03.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600079,603290}…revealed the secrets\Nin front of the magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603499,606544}Then he's one of Dad's enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:10.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606836,610881}That's right. Without the world's\Nmysteries and magic…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611090,613509}…there'd be no dreams or hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:18.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613717,618722}You're right. Eimi, I appreciate\Nyou always thinking of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618931,621100}Oh, dear, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625187,627690}Oh, brother, here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630568,633195}Hi, Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:38.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634488,638617}I've got work to do. I'll play\Nwith you in just a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:58.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654466,658262}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663267,665019}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666645,668522}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:13.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670065,673152}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685664,688959}Meimi, you have to be\Nextra careful this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689335,690920}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:35.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691128,695758}I've heard Professor Hyuga has\Na state-of-the-art security system…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695966,698177}…wired in his laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698385,701972}It just makes the job\Nmore challenging for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704225,707645}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714235,716654}HYUGA SCIENTIFIC\NRESEARCH INSTITUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:12:00.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716862,720282}I appreciate you reporters\Ncoming out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:05.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720950,725204}Professor Hyuga, there are reports\NSt. Tail has announced—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725412,728207}I don't know about any St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:14.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728415,734421}…but my computers will capture\Nany brash, petty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735130,737549}Well, just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749270,751939}You seem to be\Nmy personal bodyguards…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752147,755192}…but I told you,\NI don't need your protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755401,758320}You're not taking St. Tail\Nvery seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758529,761115}If she says she's coming, she will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:46.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761490,766245}Detective, I appreciate your concern,\Nbut I want you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766453,768580}I have enough help here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768956,770332}We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:55.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770541,775546}Since she has made her announcement,\Nit is our duty to arrest her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:13:01.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775754,781719}This laboratory has been equipped with\Nthe latest computers I've invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781927,785222}When it comes to police intuition\Nor experience…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785431,787891}…I just don't believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:13.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788100,793022}That is your prerogative, but\Nour job is to stand guard right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793230,794898}Have it your way then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795441,798319}That door is unlocked, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:22.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798527,802906}St. Tail can easily enter from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:28.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804158,808412}As part of my plan, I'm letting\NSt. Tail get in easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:34.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808620,814585}I will capture her alive and then\Nmy secret weapon will go into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815210,816462}Secret weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818047,820632}And this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820799,822176}I AM A GENIUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825512,826680}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827723,830559}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:54.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831477,834938}These will not kill or hurt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:59.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835147,839401}It's like a tranquilizer gun\Nfor live capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839902,842905}That's quite impressive.\NAnd what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:06.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843113,846367}Oh, that.\NThat's the character analyzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846784,848994}It looks like it'll fry someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:14.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849286,854375}Shall I demonstrate it?\NYou just stand there quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867805,871475}Daisuke Asuka. Born August 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871683,874436}Horoscope: Leo. Blood type: AB.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:39.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874812,879983}Fantastic! It analyzes one's personal\Ndata just by shining a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880192,883487}Does that mean\Nif the light hits St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883695,886156}…we'll learn her true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:50.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886407,890994}That's right. Today's the day\Nwe learn her true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891203,893622}Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:58.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894373,898794}Just in case, I'm going\Nto tape St. Tail's capture…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898961,901839}…and have it shown on national TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902381,904091}What a showoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904299,907970}If I am unable to capture her…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:12.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908220,912057}…I will shave my head completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921567,923527}It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931577,934705}What's that? It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:41.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935414,941170}We've got you, St. Tail!\NAssistants A, B, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943380,945716}Here I am! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950179,952181}Drat! Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:57.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953265,957686}– She'll never be able to get close!\N– Not here, at any rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960772,963275}You idiot! What are you shooting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963525,965777}You call this gun safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:10.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969615,970866}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973076,974661}…show…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976872,979249}…time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:26.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983045,986298}What are these things? Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987883,989259}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992679,994723}Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994973,998227}You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000771,1003941}Damn! I'll reveal her identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005901,1007402}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012866,1015035}I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016620,1018163}Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023835,1025629}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038433,1040352}Stop, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040561,1042187}I'll let you go today…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:26.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042396,1046733}…only because I don't want\Nto capture you with machinery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046942,1049403}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:38.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054491,1058495}– Professor! Professor!\N– The egg, the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:41.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058745,1061498}Professor, snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:45.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061707,1065043}What was I doing? That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:50.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065252,1070507}I'm sure my computer grasped\NSt. Tail's true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070716,1072551}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:55.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072759,1075470}St. Tail's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:59.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076096,1079266}Everything's in order!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081810,1083270}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083520,1086440}It's all white.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:11.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087941,1091028}Hey, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094031,1097075}This is one of those pebbles\NSt. Tail threw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097284,1100829}– What is it, Dad?\N– Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101705,1104875}Hey! Dad, isn't this a magnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:28.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105083,1108462}I get it. These machines\Ndon't take to magnets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:34.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108795,1114676}That's ridiculous!\NBut the video should show her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:45.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118680,1125020}My machines of the latest technology\Nwere thwarted by mere magnets. Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129691,1131318}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:01.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137157,1141703}What's this?\NDad, it's the egg! The egg's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141912,1144665}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145540,1147292}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148335,1152130}Yutaka, I'm going to make\Na public apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152923,1154925}About the egg being a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:21.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155509,1161014}Yes, and I'll ask everyone to help\Npreserve the island's natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:23.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161223,1163100}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165727,1167729}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168522,1171441}– Good morning!\N– Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:36.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172943,1176947}Professor Mochizuki was so very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:43.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179866,1183829}– Good morning, Meimi, Seira.\N– We'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184413,1187124}– Please let us through!\N– Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188333,1190544}Congratulations! I saw the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:55.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190752,1195590}The Apua bird's egg on\NJurassic lsland hatched, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196508,1200095}It's so neat! Please get me\Nyour father's autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200470,1202097}Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205642,1207102}DR. HYUGA WENT BALD!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211273,1213024}Good morning, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:16.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213233,1216695}Did you see this?\NLook at that bald fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:22.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216903,1222701}A bet's a bet. And he bet he could\Nreveal St. Tail's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:28.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223285,1228248}I guess that means capturing St. Tail\Nshould be left to you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:33.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228457,1233170}That's right, because I'm the best.\NI know everything about St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233378,1235630}Though she's always getting away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:40.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235922,1240677}What did you say? I had a good reason\Nfor letting her go this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241094,1243346}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246266,1249853}You said, "I don't want\Nto capture you with machinery!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250061,1252564}And you work so hard at it!
